" easy way to add lines without entering insert mode
" add line after
nmap <C-o> o<ESC>
" add line before
nmap <C-o>o O<ESC>

"fix indenting of the entire file
"use sparingly cuz it might mess stuff up
nmap <leader>s gg=G''

